The paper discusses the use of multimedia data for field studies, which falls under the category of multimedia (cs.MM). The paper also discusses the challenges of handling and processing big data, which could fall under information retrieval (cs.IR), social and information networks (cs.SI), software development (cs.SD), and computational linguistics (cs.CL).
